<plot>Conversation with Jacques Lipchitz allows the viewer to ask questions of Lipchitz and receive answers from footage stored on digital video disks that pertain to his life from his birth in Lithuania in 1891 to 1967 when he was filmed for this program in Italy working on the sculpture Bellerophon Taming Pegasus commissioned by Columbia University for The Jerome Greene School of Law.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?114903</url></doc>
